Regardless of what sports you follow, the ESPN app can keep you in the loop with up-to-the-minute scores, breaking news on signings and trades, and insightful analysis on matchups and drafts.

If you want to play fantasy sports, there areahemleagues of apps to choose from. But we think ESPN Fantasy might be the MVP. Its minimal interface stays out of our way so we can focus on draft picks, trades, and managing our lineup. But the best part? ESPNs got mini-stories on all of the hot prospects. So the more time we spend actually using the app, the better our team ends up.
